Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠子它…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出這樣的光 還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做這種傻事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你在這礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒能把半條命還給華月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這傷勢看肯定是沒得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把那孩子的身體和珠子一齊交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 一開始就打珠子和仁的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道珠子在仁的身體裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道還要故意傷害仁嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟約定好的可不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞結界後 東西就應該給我不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真是個寵孩子的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是沒想到 珠子竟然會藏在他身體裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不馬上把珠子交給那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果違背約定 那傢伙一定會來復仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月說發現仁的時候 他手上捏著奇怪的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是華月把珠子藏在仁的身體裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己的半條命一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能交給他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那傢伙來了 你贏得了他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑將半條命都給了仁的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要和華月做一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月就是因為這樣才死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為人父母義不容辭的責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月可是你的父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想用孩子的生命換取存活於世的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…又是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 馬上太陽就要落山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才珠子的光芒 一定是受了第八顆珠子的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁可能出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說仁果然是最後一顆珠子的主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你愛吃的不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直覺得 這裡就是我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那裡沒有我的容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我的歸屬地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…為我創造這一切的華月卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的存在 讓大家都變得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也是 華月也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼當初不讓我就那樣死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是華月聽到你剛才說的這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會傷心死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把結界打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逼我們出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好了就一定要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只能這樣了 雖然並非是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個良才 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我還是再等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 仁就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們一族的遺孤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易把你帶回山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還是回到人類居住的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依這個火勢 不久這座山都會被燒燬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不能待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要你自信地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那裡就是你的棲身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我和華月也會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我也要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和葉月一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前總是華月華月叫個不停的你 現在居然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為在人類的地方待久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人類的孩子 看來也不全是壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們兩兄弟 最珍愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 孩子應該也能為父母付出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不能把葉月一個人留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再尋死 不許比我這個父輩早逝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了吧 華月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群鳥為什麼要飛入熊熊大火中去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的主人在那 所以要保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 仁也在那裡咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 放開我 葉月他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是葉月的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你送到人類的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 我怎麼能丟下葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這個要怎麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回人類的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著我們的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣 是天狗和人類一起孕育的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月 事情正如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一族會疼愛人之子 是我族的天性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我們終將回到人類中去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就什麼都不要擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不離開這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為天狗的能力用盡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把珠子交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗之首 居然為了人類的孩子淪落至此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了珍愛的人 我可以隨時放棄自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你們快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月…華月…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你自信地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你生活的那裡就是你的棲身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守護這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護…我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很快也會被火焰包圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 仁一個人在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到 他就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 莊介先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也沒覆蓋過這麼大的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 展現你的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把刀怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼呆 喚風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這個勢頭看來火馬上就會熄滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又來了個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1006,710)}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉…月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…結果我還是沒能救葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼天狗之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什麼都…做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是好好地保護了這座山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 沒能帶來你想要的珠子和容器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這讓人傷腦筋的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都那樣警告你小心天狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…真是漂亮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種水好像對他來說效果不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕也完美地癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂也剝離得很完整
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 總算值得花了這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最後的珠子到了里見手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集八個靈魂卻是宿命的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是被詛咒的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也作為八個轉生靈魂的證明的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能阻止它們全部到達里見的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我趕往仁君你這裡時 看到了他的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的很像莊介先生 你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是孽緣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 跟信乃你們在一起的話就能見到那個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他總會露面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也和信乃一起去帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給葉月報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子為父母報仇 天經地義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是葉月最後交給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃說過的珠子 難道就是指這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八顆集齊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我的珠子在影那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些珠子有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會慢慢跟你講的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也丟了的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好保管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼跟奶奶說才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 栲婆婆的話沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你是天狗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:08.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}一人にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:08.03,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}不要讓我孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:11.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甘く　甘く色をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:11.54,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甜美地 綻放色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.21,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.21,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要輕易離開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:19.59,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕の命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:19.59,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.47,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.47,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:31.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}どうして君の願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:31.77,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底是為什麼 你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:37.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみの雨に打たれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:37.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖被悲傷之雨淋透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}咲いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.86,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻依舊傲然怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:45.99,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう大事なもの傷つけたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:45.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已經不能傷害重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:50.49,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その静かな笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:50.49,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只想默默守候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:54.25,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:54.25,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你那恬靜的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:58.08,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:58.08,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}伸出你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:01.63,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独さえ壊すほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:01.63,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}去打破孤寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.76,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉の時も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.76,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到終結之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:07.64,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:07.64,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:12.72,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:12.72,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有你能照亮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:17.81,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}ただ一つの光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:17.81,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}是我唯一的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 我和你確實相像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是一模一樣也毫不誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 言行舉止可別模仿我
